itunes:title: Success Is The Best Revenge
title: Success Is The Best Revenge
description:
In this episode Jessi expands on her story and gives advice on how to handle situations of conflict whether online or in person. Everyone goes through hard times but Jessi explains why it's best to let those times motivate you to do better rather than letting them bring you down. We hope this episode helps if your going through a similar situation!
